---
layout: base.njk
title: "Limavady High School - Virtual Tour Case Study"
description: "How 360° virtual tours transformed student engagement and accessibility at Limavady High School"
client: "Limavady High School"
service: "Educational Virtual Tours"
sector: "Education"
heroImage: "images/limavady-1.png"
secondaryImage: "images/limavady-2.png"
testimonialQuote: "The virtual tour has transformed how we engage with prospective families. It's increased our reach significantly and allows parents and students to get a genuine feel for our school environment before they visit."
testimonialAuthor: "Sarah Mitchell"
testimonialTitle: "Head of Admissions, Limavady High School"
stats:
  - number: "150%"
    label: "Increase in Virtual Visits"
  - number: "40%"
    label: "Reduction in Physical Tour Requests"
  - number: "85%"
    label: "User Satisfaction Rating"
tags: ["case-studies", "education", "virtual-tours"]
permalink: "/case-studies/limavady-high-school/"
---

<section class="luxury-case-study">
  <div
    class="luxury-case-study-container">
    <!-- Hero Header Section -->
    <div class="luxury-case-study-hero">
      <div class="luxury-case-study-meta">
        <span class="luxury-case-study-badge">Case Study</span>
        <div class="luxury-case-study-details">
          <div class="luxury-case-study-detail">
            <span class="luxury-detail-label">Client</span>
            <span class="luxury-detail-value">{{ client }}</span>
          </div>
          <div class="luxury-case-study-detail">
            <span class="luxury-detail-label">Service</span>
            <span class="luxury-detail-value">{{ service }}</span>
          </div>
          <div class="luxury-case-study-detail">
            <span class="luxury-detail-label">Sector</span>
            <span class="luxury-detail-value">{{ sector }}</span>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
      <h1 class="luxury-case-study-title">Transforming Education: Virtual Tours at
      {{ client }}</h1>
      <p class="luxury-case-study-subtitle">{{ description }}</p>
    </div>
    <!-- Main Image Section -->
    <div class="luxury-case-study-image">
      <img src="{{ heroImage }}" alt="{{ client }} Virtual Tour"/>
      <div class="luxury-image-overlay"></div>
    </div>
    <!-- Project Description -->
    <div class="luxury-case-study-content">
      <div class="luxury-content-section">
        <h2>Project Overview</h2>
        <p>{{ client }} partnered with 360spaces to create an immersive virtual tour experience that showcases their
          state-of-the-art facilities, vibrant learning environments, and unique educational atmosphere. This comprehensive
          digital solution allows prospective students and families to explore the school from anywhere, at any time.</p>
        <p>The virtual tour captures every aspect of school life - from modern classrooms and science laboratories to sports
          facilities and common areas - providing an authentic feel for what makes
          {{ client }} a premier educational destination.</p>
      </div>
      <div class="luxury-content-section">
        <h2>The Challenge</h2>
        <p>Like many educational institutions, {{ client }} faced the challenge of effectively showcasing their facilities to
          prospective students and families who couldn't always visit in person. Traditional photography and brochures couldn't
          capture the full scale and atmosphere of their impressive campus.</p>
        <p>The school needed a solution that would increase accessibility, reduce the burden on staff for individual tours, and
          provide a compelling digital experience that truly represented their educational excellence.</p>
      </div>
      <div class="luxury-content-section">
        <h2>Our Solution</h2>
        <p>We developed a comprehensive virtual tour that brings {{ client }}'s campus to life through cutting-edge 360°
          technology. The solution includes:</p>
        <ul class="luxury-feature-list">
          <li>Interactive navigation through all key areas of the school</li>
          <li>Integrated multimedia content including videos and information points</li>
          <li>Mobile-responsive design for access on any device</li>
          <li>Accessibility features ensuring inclusive access for all users</li>
          <li>Seamless integration with the school's existing website</li>
        </ul>
      </div>
      <!-- Testimonial Section -->
      <div class="luxury-testimonial-section">
        <div class="luxury-testimonial-content">
          <blockquote class="luxury-testimonial-quote">{{ testimonialQuote }}</blockquote>
          <div class="luxury-testimonial-author">
            <div class="luxury-author-info">
              <span class="luxury-author-name">{{ testimonialAuthor }}</span>
              <span class="luxury-author-title">{{ testimonialTitle }}</span>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
      <!-- Results Section -->
      <div class="luxury-content-section">
        <h2>Results</h2>
        <div class="luxury-results-grid">
          {% for stat in stats %}
            <div class="luxury-result-stat">
              <div class="luxury-stat-number">{{ stat.number }}</div>
              <div class="luxury-stat-label">{{ stat.label }}</div>
            </div>
          {% endfor %}
        </div>
      </div>
      <!-- Additional Image -->
      {% if secondaryImage %}
        <div class="luxury-case-study-image luxury-secondary-image">
          <img src="{{ secondaryImage }}" alt="{{ client }} Additional View"/>
          <div class="luxury-image-caption">
            <p>Students and families can explore modern classrooms and specialized learning spaces through our immersive virtual
              tour experience.</p>
          </div>
        </div>
      {% endif %}
      <!-- Call to Action -->
      <div class="luxury-case-study-cta">
        <h3>Ready to Transform Your Institution?</h3>
        <p>See how 360° virtual tours can enhance your educational environment and improve accessibility for prospective
          students and families.</p>
        <a href="https://cal.com/karl-mcclelland-m2ppu8/" class="luxury-cta-button" target="_blank" rel="noopener">
          <span>Schedule a Consultation</span>
          <svg viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg">
            <path
              d="M7 17L17 7M17 7H7M17 7V17"
              stroke="currentColor"
              stroke-width="2"
              stroke-linecap="round"
              stroke-linejoin="round"/>
          </svg>
        </a>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>